      "Title": "SmarterLink.Core.Attributes.PayloadTypeNameAttribute",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/SmarterLink.Core.Attributes.PayloadTypeNameAttribute.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Specifies the stable wire name for a SmarterLink protocol payload type.\nWhen present, this name is used in the protocol header's <code>payloadType</code> field,\nthe MQTT topic event segment, and documentation schema exports — in place of the\nC# type name. This decouples the wire protocol name from the C# identifier, so\ntypes can be renamed without breaking protocol compatibility.</p>\n"
    },
